    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Organize &amp; De-clutter</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/1c0fbe67c710094b48bb08d7ff284a2b.poster.avif?t=1749654015\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/1c0fbe67c710094b48bb08d7ff284a2b.webm?t=1749654015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/1c0fbe67c710094b48bb08d7ff284a2b.mp4?t=1749654015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform messy desks into dream setups as the Setup Savior! A  game about organization, refurnishing, and fulfillment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your interior design business helping people of all kinds improve their spaces. Manage wants, needs, and budgets, while working towards your dreams of making it big in the city.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Transform &amp; Build Setups</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/3a45d42e0be84317f771cb56680987a1.poster.avif?t=1749654015\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/3a45d42e0be84317f771cb56680987a1.webm?t=1749654015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/3a45d42e0be84317f771cb56680987a1.mp4?t=1749654015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each client provides a puzzle where organization meets creativity - whether it be work spaces, gaming setups, or lounge areas. Make it work, and make it look good, as you fulfill your creative vision without breaking the budget. Concrete objectives serve as an inspiration to get you going, and not a chain around your leg!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Jump Right In<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/520e68ad3c7ad8d436df39df0949cddc.poster.avif?t=1749654015\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/520e68ad3c7ad8d436df39df0949cddc.webm?t=1749654015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/520e68ad3c7ad8d436df39df0949cddc.mp4?t=1749654015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a strong focus on intuitive and satisfying interactions the game becomes a platform to funnel your creative energy. From planning with an overview to experiencing in first person, you really get a feel for your work!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not a fan of limits? Jump into <strong>Sandbox</strong> <strong>Mode</strong> and go wild without concerns of price or objectives, and share your amazing creations with the world!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rearrange &amp; Unpack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/f30cc2361bdfd695d8ec21c59ef3d4df.poster.avif?t=1749654015\" width=800 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/f30cc2361bdfd695d8ec21c59ef3d4df.webm?t=1749654015\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230170/extras/f30cc2361bdfd695d8ec21c59ef3d4df.mp4?t=1749654015\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for fans of Unpacking's satisfying organization and The Sims' creative freedom, Setup Savior brings a fresh take on the cozy game genre, combining creative interior design with concrete gameplay goals!</p>",
